een thereabouts in all of his 4 starts this prep. He stuck on well at Ascot over the mile for fourth, and the rise in trip looks ideal. He has not missed a placing in 3 starts over this trip, and with some luck from a tricky gate, he is the one to beat for us. 2. OUTSPOKEN LAD was not far away off a wide gate in the Albany Cup 6-days ago, and his prior Ascot run was solid. He gets his best draw in a while, and with a cosy run, he can produce a big finish. Each-way. 1. SOWAR is a durable veteran who has been back to the trials since finishing out of the money, but not far off them in the Listed Detonator Stakes at Ascot 7 weeks ago. The blinkers go back on, and if he doesn't need the run, he could well make a winning track debut. 11. WHAT A PRINCE likes to have his own way in front, and he has the right draw to take up the lead early on here. He has won his only start over this trip, and on this course he may take plenty of pegging back.\",\"runners\":[4,2,1,11],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Alex Vlahos","tipRunnerNumbers":[4,11,1,2]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,2,11,1]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,11,4,9]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,5,6,4]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,5,11]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,4,2,1]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,2,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,4,11,1]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"NGN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"NGN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"NGN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"NGN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"NGN","raceType":"R"}},